1. Information We Collect

StockPilot does not collect, store, or share any personal or non-personal user data.

No personal information (such as name, email address, or phone number) is collected.

No financial information is collected.

No device data, usage data, or analytics data is collected.

No location data is collected.

2. Data Storage

All data generated while using StockPilot remains entirely on your device. The App does not transmit any data to external servers or third parties.

3. Third-Party Services

StockPilot does not use any third-party services that collect user data, including:

Analytics services

Advertising networks

External tracking tools

4. Data Sharing

Because no data is collected, no user data is shared with any third parties.

5. Security

Since StockPilot does not collect or transmit user data, there is no risk of data exposure from external storage or servers. Any information you input remains securely on your local device.

6. Children’s Privacy

StockPilot does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13. Since no data is collected, the App is compliant with applicable child privacy standards.

